once upon a time there lived a monkey who resided in a tree,which was on the banks of river . in that river there lived a Crocodile and his wife . one day the Crocodile came to the banks of the river
and rested under the tree . the kind hearted monkey give him some fruits. 
the Crocodile came back for more fruits as he loved them.
as the days passed by, the Crocodile and monkey became good friends.
